public interface GenericService<T>
A generic service interface providing CRUD operations for entities of type T.

  • Method Details

    • search

      List<T> search(String query, Integer offset, Integer size, String orderby, String orderType)
      Searches for entities based on the provided query, offset, size, orderby, and orderType.
      Parameters:
      query - The search query.
      offset - The offset for pagination.
      size - The maximum number of entities to retrieve.
      orderby - The field to order the results by.
      orderType - The type of order (e.g., "asc" or "desc").
      Returns:
      A list of entities matching the search criteria.

      String auditHistory(int id, Integer limit, Integer skip)
      Retrieves the audit history of an entity.
      Parameters:
      id - The identifier of the entity.
      limit - The maximum number of audit entries to retrieve.
      skip - The number of audit entries to skip.
      Returns:
      The audit history of the entity as a string.
